author: Alessandra Foresto
title: Jennifer Lopez Playlist
text:
Get ready to stand up and, like J Lo says herself, shake it! We went back through the archives of Jennifer Lopez 's best songs, from her first album in 1999 to her most recent tune "Ain't Your Mama" and compiled the ultimate playlist that'll get you off your seat and have you dancing and singing in mere seconds.
The task was no small feat â€” the queen of Latin pop has given us tons of songs that will forever be etched in our minds and bodies as iconic. Who could ever forget the chorus to "Let's Get Loud" or the on-point lyrics to "Jenny From the Block"? So, without fearther ado, these are the 20 tunes we're calling J Lo's best.
